data.title: Perfectly located condo in Annandale VA, 3332 Woodburn Village Drive #33, Annandale, VA!
data.meta_description: Perfectly located condo in Woodburn Village of Annandale Virginia!
data.text:
Welcome to your next investment property. This is a perfect addition to your investment portfolio! This home features two bedrooms and one bathroom. It is located in the charming community of Woodburn Village in Annandale, VA.

Come check out this 3rd floor condominium with a charming balcony and spacious kitchen. This condo is close to major shopping destinations and parkland. Luckily, this great property already comes with a tenant and a signed lease through June of 2021!

Let your imagination and earning potential go wild with all the possibilities.

This exciting opportunity could be yours!!
